# GSD Project Configuration Rules

## Planning System Structure

### Directory Organization
```
.planning/
├── config.json              # GSD workflow configuration
├── PROJECT.md               # Project overview and goals
├── REQUIREMENTS.md          # Detailed requirements
├── ROADMAP.md              # Project phases and milestones
├── STATE.md                # Current project state
├── ALL-PHASES-UI-REVIEW.md  # UI review across phases
├── todos/                  # Todo management
│   ├── completed/          # Completed tasks
│   ├── done/              # Done tasks
│   └── pending/           # Pending tasks
├── codebase/              # Codebase analysis
├── debug/                 # Debug information
├── notes/                 # Project notes
├── phases/               # Phase-specific planning
└── quick/                # Quick task planning
```

### Configuration Schema
**`.planning/config.json`** defines:
- **Model profile**: Quality-focused execution
- **Branching strategy**: GSD-specific branch templates
- **Workflow phases**: Research, plan check, verifier, UI phase
- **Hooks**: Context warnings and validation
- **Granularity**: Standard task sizing

### Branch Templates
```javascript
// Phase branches
"gsd/phase-{phase}-{slug}"

// Milestone branches  
"gsd/{milestone}-{slug}"

// Quick tasks (no template)
null
```

