## Workflow Configuration

### Enabled Workflow Features
- ✅ **Research**: Pre-change investigation
- ✅ **Plan Check**: Validation before execution
- ✅ **Verifier**: Post-change verification
- ✅ **UI Phase**: UI-specific safety gates
- ✅ **Auto Advance**: Automatic phase progression
- ✅ **Node Repair**: Self-healing capability (budget: 2)
- ✅ **UI Safety Gate**: UI change protection

### Discussion Mode
- **Mode**: "discuss" - collaborative decision making
- **Skip Discuss**: false - always discuss when needed
- **Research Before Questions**: false - direct interaction allowed

### Agent Skills
- Empty object `{}` - no custom agent skills configured
- **Resolve Model IDs**: "omit" - exclude model identifiers
- **Mode**: "yolo" - aggressive execution
- **Granularity**: "standard" - normal task sizing

