## Project Planning Documents

### Core Documents
- **PROJECT.md**: Project overview, constraints, core value
- **REQUIREMENTS.md**: Detailed functional requirements
- **ROADMAP.md**: Phase-by-phase project roadmap
- **STATE.md**: Current project state and status
- **ALL-PHASES-UI-REVIEW.md**: Cross-phase UI consistency

### GSD Markers
Documents use GSD markers for structured content:
```html
<!-- GSD:project-start source:PROJECT.md -->
<!-- GSD:stack-start source:codebase/STACK.md -->
<!-- GSD:conventions-start source:CONVENTIONS.md -->
<!-- GSD:architecture-start source:ARCHITECTURE.md -->
<!-- GSD:workflow-start source:GSD defaults -->
<!-- GSD:profile-start -->
```

### Developer Profile
- **Status**: Not yet configured
- **Command**: `/gsd-profile-user` to generate profile
- **Management**: Automated by `generate-claude-profile`
- **Warning**: Do not edit manually

